node.text:
Day 3: Houston Cigar Week™️ Presents .. Welcome 2 Houston .. Sponsored by 2 Houston Based Cigar Companies .. @ovcigars Cigars The Fastest Growing Cigar Company In The World & The Legendary @masculino_cigars Houston 1st Black Owned Boutique Cigar Company .. Thank You 🙏 Celebrity @therealchefshay for Catering Our VIP Lunch .. We Want To Thank Everyone For Attending Houston Cigar Week™️ .. The Week Wouldn’t of Special Without Every SOTL 💋💨 & BOTL 🍃💨 Who Attended .. See You Next Year .. Memorial Day Weekend .. May 24th - May 29th 2022 .. @houstoncigarweek

#Repost @houstoncigarlife
・・・
@houstoncigarweek Ladies Night is going to be one epic cigar party with 30 #cigar vendors, @edreedhof20 dropping a guest DJ set along with @edlover as our celebrity host. 

Most importantly it'll be a celebration for all the smart, classy and beautiful #SOTL's from all over the country... #atl #htx #lasvegas #miami #dallas #losangeles #newyork

Hundreds of tickets have been sold and it's possible we'll reach capacity, so DM @houstoncigarweek now for details, tickets and bottle service. 

If you haven't seen the venue, check out @clehouston. The patio on its own is dope af, but the pool just adds a next level vibe. 

Come enjoy #cigars with the fam on May 28th for #Houston Cigar Week.

#houstoncigarlife #hcw2021 #houstoncigarweek
